query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS checklistResults (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  checklistId INT NOT NULL,
  itemId INT NOT NULL,
  result ENUM('pass', 'fail', 'na') NOT NULL,
  comment TEXT,
  photoUrls TEXT,
  inspectedBy INT NOT NULL,
  inspectedAt TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  INDEX checklistIdx (checklistId),
  INDEX itemIdx (itemId)
);
